<section class="section section--green">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-content">
      <p class="why-content__body">Most accessibility consultants come from a technology background. Laura Cantagallo&rsquo;s experience is rooted in special education and assistive technology. With 16 years of experience supporting students with diverse learning and access needs, Laura brings a perspective that many accessibility consultants do not. She has worked directly with students who use screen readers, AAC devices, and other assistive technologies, giving her a strong understanding of how digital barriers affect real people in real settings. What sets LC Education Consulting apart is a combination of educational experience, assistive technology expertise, and digital accessibility knowledge grounded in real-world practice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

